AttributeDefinition
public static enum AttributeDefinition.UserInterfaceInputType
extends java.lang.Enum<AttributeDefinition.UserInterfaceInputType>

The UserInterfaceInputType enumeration specifies how an attribute should be edited in the user interface. A null value means that the attribute cannot be edited.
